---
// Trust Signals Component - Astro (zero-JS)
---

<section class="w-full py-20 px-4 bg-slate-50">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Brand Partners -->
    <div class="mb-20">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Marcas de Confianza</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600">Especialistas en reparación de las marcas más reconocidas del mundo</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-5">
        <!-- Apple -->
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 p-5 flex flex-col items-center gap-4 border border-slate-100 hover:border-slate-200 hover:-translate-y-1">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-[#000000] flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg class="w-9 h-9 text-white" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M18.71 19.5c-.83 1.24-1.71 2.45-3.05 2.47-1.34.03-1.77-.79-3.29-.79-1.53 0-2 .77-3.27.82-1.31.05-2.3-1.32-3.14-2.53C4.25 17 2.94 12.45 4.7 9.39c.87-1.52 2.43-2.48 4.12-2.51 1.28-.02 2.5.87 3.29.87.78 0 2.26-1.07 3.8-.91.65.03 2.47.26 3.64 1.98-.09.06-2.17 1.28-2.15 3.81.03 3.02 2.65 4.03 2.68 4.04-.03.07-.42 1.44-1.38 2.83M13 3.5c.67-.82 1.78-1.39 2.7-1.42.07 1.07-.28 2.16-.94 2.96-.66.8-1.73 1.36-2.76 1.34-.11-1.04.28-2.12 1-2.88z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 tracking-wider uppercase">Apple</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Samsung -->
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 p-5 flex flex-col items-center gap-4 border border-slate-100 hover:border-slate-200 hover:-translate-y-1">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-[#1428A0] flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg class="w-9 h-9 text-white" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <rect x="6" y="2" width="12" height="20" rx="2.5" />
              <circle cx="12" cy="19" r="1.2" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" />
              <path d="M8.5 6h7" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 tracking-wider uppercase">Samsung</span>
        </div>

        <!-- HP -->
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 p-5 flex flex-col items-center gap-4 border border-slate-100 hover:border-slate-200 hover:-translate-y-1">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-[#0096D6] flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg class="w-9 h-9 text-white" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <rect x="3" y="10" width="18" height="8" rx="1.5" />
              <path d="M5 10V7a2 2 0 012-2h10a2 2 0 012 2v3" />
              <rect x="7" y="13" width="10" height="2" rx="0.5" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 tracking-wider uppercase">HP</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Lenovo -->
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 p-5 flex flex-col items-center gap-4 border border-slate-100 hover:border-slate-200 hover:-translate-y-1">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-[#E2231A] flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg class="w-9 h-9 text-white" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <rect x="4" y="4" width="16" height="16" rx="2" />
              <path d="M8 8h3l2.5 8L16 8h3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
              <path d="M6 16h3l1-4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 tracking-wider uppercase">Lenovo</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Nintendo -->
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 p-5 flex flex-col items-center gap-4 border border-slate-100 hover:border-slate-200 hover:-translate-y-1">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-[#E60012] flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg class="w-9 h-9 text-white" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <rect x="3" y="5" width="7" height="14" rx="1.5" />
              <rect x="14" y="5" width="7" height="14" rx="1.5" />
              <circle cx="6.5" cy="12" r="1.2" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" />
              <circle cx="17.5" cy="12" r="1.2" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" />
              <circle cx="6.5" cy="16" r="0.8" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 tracking-wider uppercase">Nintendo</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Sony PlayStation -->
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 p-5 flex flex-col items-center gap-4 border border-slate-100 hover:border-slate-200 hover:-translate-y-1">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-[#000000] flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg class="w-9 h-9 text-white" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <rect x="3" y="7" width="18" height="12" rx="4" />
              <circle cx="8.5" cy="13" r="1.5" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" />
              <circle cx="15.5" cy="13" r="1.5" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" />
              <path d="M12 10v5" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" />
              <path d="M10.5 12h3" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 tracking-wider uppercase">Sony</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Microsoft -->
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 p-5 flex flex-col items-center gap-4 border border-slate-100 hover:border-slate-200 hover:-translate-y-1">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-[#00A4EF] flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg class="w-9 h-9" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <rect x="4" y="4" width="7.5" height="7.5" rx="1" fill="#F25022" />
              <rect x="12.5" y="4" width="7.5" height="7.5" rx="1" fill="#7FBA00" />
              <rect x="4" y="12.5" width="7.5" height="7.5" rx="1" fill="#00A4EF" />
              <rect x="12.5" y="12.5" width="7.5" height="7.5" rx="1" fill="#FFB900" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 tracking-wider uppercase">Microsoft</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Motorola -->
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 p-5 flex flex-col items-center gap-4 border border-slate-100 hover:border-slate-200 hover:-translate-y-1">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-[#E1140A] flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg class="w-9 h-9 text-white" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2">
              <path d="M12 4L4 20h4l4-8 4 8h4L12 4z" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" />
              <path d="M12 4L4 20h4l4-8 4 8h4L12 4z" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="0.5" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 tracking-wider uppercase">Motorola</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Xiaomi -->
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 p-5 flex flex-col items-center gap-4 border border-slate-100 hover:border-slate-200 hover:-translate-y-1">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-[#FF6900] flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg class="w-9 h-9 text-white" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
              <rect x="5" y="4" width="6" height="16" rx="1" />
              <rect x="13" y="4" width="6" height="16" rx="1" />
              <rect x="11" y="4" width="4" height="5" rx="1" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 tracking-wider uppercase">Xiaomi</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 15 Years Badge -->
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-teal-600 rounded-lg p-12 text-white text-center mb-20">
      <div class="text-6xl font-bold mb-4">16 Años</div>
      <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">de Excelencia</h3>
      <p class="text-xl opacity-90">
        Sirviendo a la comunidad de Los Mochis con servicios de reparación confiables y profesionales
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Testimonials -->
    <div>
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Testimonios de Clientes</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 shadow-md border-l-4 border-blue-600">
          <div class="flex gap-1 mb-4">
            <span class="text-yellow-400">★</span>
            <span class="text-yellow-400">★</span>
            <span class="text-yellow-400">★</span>
            <span class="text-yellow-400">★</span>
            <span class="text-yellow-400">★</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
            "¡Excelente servicio! Me repararon la pantalla del celular en solo 2 horas. Muy profesionales y precios justos. ¡Altamente recomendados!"
          </p>
          <p class="font-semibold text-slate-900">María González</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 shadow-md border-l-4 border-teal-600">
          <div class="flex gap-1 mb-4">
            <span class="text-yellow-400">★</span>
            <span class="text-yellow-400">★</span>
            <span class="text-yellow-400">★</span>
            <span class="text-yellow-400">★</span>
            <span class="text-yellow-400">★</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
            "Llevé mi laptop con el disco duro dañado y la dejaron como nueva. Excelentes técnicos y precios honestos."
          </p>
          <p class="font-semibold text-slate-900">Carlos Rodríguez</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 shadow-md border-l-4 border-blue-500">
          <div class="flex gap-1 mb-4">
            <span class="text-yellow-400">★</span>
            <span class="text-yellow-400">★</span>
            <span class="text-yellow-400">★</span>
            <span class="text-yellow-400">★</span>
            <span class="text-yellow-400">★</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
            "Llevan años reparando las computadoras de nuestro negocio. Confiables, rápidos y honestos. ¡Gracias CDSE!"
          </p>
          <p class="font-semibold text-slate-900">Jorge Sánchez</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
